-h%E1%BB%8Dc-Xu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0n-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-cu3ZcTO_yjd8I_itJ-xI_Q">Thù Đạo Khê thái học “Xuân hàn” vận - 酬道溪太學春寒韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-L%E1%BB%85-b%E1%BB%99-Ch%E1%BB%A7-s%E1%BB%B1-%C4%90a-S%C4%A9-L%C3%AA-%C4%91%C3%A0i-gi%E1%BA%A3-m%C3%A3n-h%E1%BB%93i-kinh/poem-CXfYZd4HdEQZUW_h84t1NQ">Tiễn Lễ bộ Chủ sự Đa Sĩ Lê đài giả mãn hồi kinh - 餞禮部主事多士黎臺假滿回京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch-s%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0/poem-yezq_vKXfawT8Q8cIlAS9A">Ức tích sơn cư - 憶昔山居</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chi%C3%AAm-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-CF4h4cy0l6rugNx2hdZfpQ">Chiêm Đồng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Th%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2n/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-l%E1%BB%87/poem-SNSbg97GRcY2FQqS5-CAQg">Xuân nhật hoài lệ - 春日懷淚</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Th%E1%BB%A5c-Ch%C3%A2n/author-i-czuf5WvTrcNJ1FAmZhMw">Chu Thục Chân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
